WEBVTT

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:02.240
and that means that we all have something
to worry about from surveillance.

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:06.016
Surveillance means
government collection and use

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:09.256
of private and sensitive data about us.

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:11.216
And surveillance is essential

00:01:11.240 --> 00:01:14.336
to law enforcement
and to national security.

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:16.336
But the history of surveillance

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:19.856
is one that includes surveillance abuses

00:01:19.880 --> 00:01:23.336
where this sensitive information
has been used against people

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:24.896
because of their race,

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:26.696
their national origin,

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:28.776
their sexual orientation,

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:31.976
and in particular,
because of their activism,